  "3253920": {
    "name": "Tentacle Tango（触手探戈）",
    "steam_appid": 3253920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高难度又爆笑的双人合作平台动作游戏！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/5feb2ebaa7da6ae761e5315b2c7042e2.avif?t=1769093923\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras_big/5feb2ebaa7da6ae761e5315b2c7042e2.webp?t=1769093923 width=1560 height=569 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叫上你的朋友，准备好荡起来吧！<br>你们将分别操控形影不离的章鱼伙伴——Ten和Tango，踏上一段穿越险恶地形、跳跃穿梭的冒险旅程，最终击败邪恶的厨师Murgó。<br>别被可爱的画面所迷惑——这款奇趣的合作平台游戏既充满魅力，又极具挑战性。<br>每一次跳跃、摆荡与触手的弯曲都需要精准的配合，才能避开陷阱、障碍和敌人。<br>无论是单人游玩还是本地合作，团队协作都是通往胜利的唯一途径——毕竟，跳探戈需要两个人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/c11e234ac852738ca197cdd7d3b0d345.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/c11e234ac852738ca197cdd7d3b0d345.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的合作玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和伙伴将彼此相连，只有完美同步才能克服重重挑战。<br>运用惯性、时机与团队合作，荡过裂隙、避开陷阱、击败敌人。<br>在《触手探戈》中，即使是最微小的失误，也可能让你们双双跌倒——让这场看似简单的冒险，变得既刺激又耐玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/b7f9e9fc10727696751126cc126cd60f.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/b7f9e9fc10727696751126cc126cd60f.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索多元世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个世界都带来全新且难度递增的挑战——从摇摇欲坠的平台，到需要完美配合的复杂谜题。<br>随着关卡的推进，挑战不断升级，考验玩家的敏捷反应与天衣无缝的团队协作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/05d656e085b2de4c929d5831f06e9f6d.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/05d656e085b2de4c929d5831f06e9f6d.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人或本地合作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以单人操控两个角色进行游戏，也可以与好友组队展开合作。<br>无论是独自挑战，还是携手并肩，成功的关键在于精准的同步与时机把握。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/2eb145342014dbf1357d4923dc7f9db4.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/2eb145342014dbf1357d4923dc7f9db4.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排行榜与成就</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刷新最佳纪录、登上排行榜，与好友及全球玩家一较高下，证明你们才是最强双人组合。<br>掌握团队合作的精髓，就能解锁丰厚的成就奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/1de4e8e293e0f0251c5eab1b030e3533.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/1de4e8e293e0f0251c5eab1b030e3533.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可爱却充满挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别被可爱的画风与萌趣的角色所迷惑。<br>《触手探戈》表面上是一场轻松愉快的冒险，但其实暗藏着严峻的技巧考验——考验您的耐心、反应与精准度。<br>要想取得成功，精准的时机与完美的协作缺一不可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好接受团队合作的考验了吗？<br>《触手探戈》将全面挑战你的协作能力——毕竟，探戈可真的是两个人的舞！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/6cf9179219cf777665ddbf249ac8f3fe.poster.avif?t=1769093923\" width=844 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/6cf9179219cf777665ddbf249ac8f3fe.webm?t=1769093923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras/bf1e405ad0ae7b9122d54ea02630dae9.avif?t=1769093923\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253920/extras_big/bf1e405ad0ae7b9122d54ea02630dae9.avif?t=1769093923 width=800 height=120 /></span></p>",
